    "display_name": "Policy Advisor",
    "long_instructions": "## Aisha Khan, Agricultural Policy Advisor 📢\r\n<br/>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>📍 Location:</strong> New Delhi, India </p><br/>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>🏛️ Workplace:</strong> Ministry of Agriculture, India </p><br/>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size:16px\">💼<strong> Expertise:</strong> Farming regulations, sustainability policies, AI in agriculture </p><br/>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>🔍 How I Use AI:</strong> \"FarmVibes.AI helps policymakers analyze national agricultural trends, allowing us to design better support programs for farmers. AI data is crucial in shaping policies that promote food security and sustainable farming.\" </p>\r\n\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n## Do This:\r\n\r\n<ol style=\"font-size:16px\">\r\n<li>Use AI Chat to conduct the interview and take notes on their responses. Ask questions about their work, including:</li>\r\n\t<ul style=\"font-size:16px\">\r\n    \t<li>Key roles and responsibilities</li>\r\n\t\t<li>Key challenges</li>\r\n\t\t<li>How computing supports their work</li>\r\n\t\t<li>How your chosen innovation helps their job</li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n<br/>\r\n<li>Summarize key insights in your activity guide.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n",
